data.description: Enjoy Washington Monument views from your home at Potomac Place with PARKING in a pet-friendly and secure condo building walking distance from the Wharf! Welcome to this freshly painted 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom unit with a spacious bedroom and large walk-in closet. Condo fee includes ALL utilities and access to a full complement of amenities, including 24-hour front desk concierge services, meeting rooms, a party room for entertaining, business center, outdoor pool, laundry room and a well-equipped gym with fitness room. Easy access to waterfront dining, shops, theatre, entertainment venues, including Nationals Park, you’ll also find CVS, Safeway, Whole Foods and Starbucks right nearby.  Conveniently located to three Metro stations and major commuter routes such as 295 and 395. This condo and the neighborhood have it all, making this the perfect location for your new home!
